  <dc:creator>sun123zxy </dc:creator>
  <link>https://blog.sun123zxy.top/posts/20260426-classic-nilp-orbit/</link>
  <description><![CDATA[ 所谓经典李代数，即是单李代数中寄居在线性李代数 <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?%5Cmathfrak%7Bgl%7D_n"> 中 <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?%5Cmathfrak%7Bsl%7D_n">、<img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?%5Cmathfrak%7Bso%7D_n"> 和 <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?%5Cmathfrak%7Bsp%7D_%7B2n%7D">．其中 <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?A_n"> 型是 <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?%5Cmathfrak%7Bsl%7D_%7Bn+1%7D">，<img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?B_n"> 型是 <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?%5Cmathfrak%7Bso%7D_%7B2n+1%7D">，<img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?C_n"> 型是 <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?%5Cmathfrak%7Bsp%7D_%7B2n%7D">，<img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?D_n"> 型是 <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?%5Cmathfrak%7Bso%7D_%7B2n%7D">．其中 <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?%5Cmathfrak%7Bsl%7D_n"> 的幂零轨道已经由 Jordan 型分类，本篇主要关心 <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?%5Cmathfrak%7Bso%7D_n"> 和 <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?%5Cmathfrak%7Bsp%7D_%7B2n%7D"> 中的幂零轨道． ]]></description>
  <category>math</category>
